**Cedar Ridge Christian Church**
100 W. Albany St.
Broken Arrow, OK 74012
[Get Directions](https://maps.google.com){: .btn}
[Learn More About Us](/about){: .btn .secondary}

## WHAT DO WE BELIEVE?
We are followers of Jesus Christ first and foremost. We have a high view of Scripture and are passionate about learning and living out God's Word. We would be considered both conservative in our theology and contemporary in our approach to ministry.
[What We Believe](/beliefs){: .btn}

## HOW DO I GET INVOLVED?
That's easy! As you find a worship service, you will also want to find a Small Group on Sunday mornings. Small Groups help us make a large church smaller as we connect to each other, build relationships, and do life together. There are plenty of ways to volunteer at CRCC and we will help you find a great place to serve. We also have a new members class to help you make all the right connections with us.
[Click Here to Find Your Next Step](/get-involved){: .btn .secondary}
